{
  "stem": "12674.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was the head of the Judenrat in Theresienstadt when I was there in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so-- so I was involved with my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't have-- I was very-- I could sing all the songs and say all the prayers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I prayed every morning and I prayed every night before I went to bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the only thing I didn't do was when I saw the movies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all kneeling down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to my mother, why don't we kneel down?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I ?] says, because we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So what was it like at first to hear the Nazi doctrine about Jews?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] What was it like?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a nightmare because, number one, on Friday night, the street that I lived in a side street of was one of the main entry points leading to the inner city in Vienna. where-- where they were coming in.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were standing 10 deep on the street, yelling, Heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The population of Vienna was out in force, and they were all welcoming him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was an enthusiastic reception.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all very, very happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is the-- that was the-- a Jew-- even before, from after the Social Democrats went out in 1932, we had a sort of a little revolution.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Christian Socialist Party, a Jew could not have a state position.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A Jew could not be a policeman or a teacher or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there-- there was already prejudice for-- against Jews in Austria before that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the schools were Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the children said 'Our Father' when they started to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every classroom had a crucifix in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was nothing special.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
